* goodreads script : progress bar/status report 52 books a year goal
* hog : hunt the disk hog utility 
  hog                # report of current tracked dirs
  hog info .         # report of '.' dir
  hog track .        # start tracking (recursive) the '.' dir
  hog untrack .      # remove/exclude the '.' dir from tracking
  hog cron           # cron activities
  -------------------------------------------------------------
